  <title>pm-utils-&pm-utils-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      The Power Management Utilities is a small collection of scripts to suspend
      and hibernate computer that can be used to run user supplied scripts on
      suspend and resume.
    </para>

